    {'id': 'q_chunk2_005', 'topic': 'Dimensional Analysis', 'sub_concept': 'Force expressions', 'difficulty_level': 0.5, 'question_text': 'If the centripetal force is of the form m^α v^b r^c, find the values of α, b and c.', 'options': [], 'correct_option_index': None, 'solution_logic': 'Force dimension ML^-1 T^-2. Equating exponents gives α=1, b=2, c=-1.'
