    {'id': 'q_chunk2_030', 'topic': 'Dimensional Analysis', 'sub_concept': 'Thermodynamics', 'difficulty_level': 0.5, 'question_text': 'Find the dimensions of (a) specific heat capacity c, (b) coefficient of linear expansion α and (c) gas constant R. Some equations involving these quantities are Q = m c (T2 - T1), I_t = l0 [
