    {'id': 'q_chunk2_033', 'topic': 'Unit conversion', 'sub_concept': 'Speed conversion', 'difficulty_level': 0.3, 'question_text': 'The average speed of a snail is 0.020 miles/hour and that of a leopard is 70 miles/hour. Convert these speeds in SI units.', 'options': [], 'correct_option_index': None, 'solution_logic': 'Snail: 0.020 mi/h ≈ 0.0089 m/s; Leopard: 70 mi/h ≈ 31 m/s.'
